                    <img src="/patric/images/bv-brc/patric-logo.png" alt="PATRIC Logo">
                    <p>The Pathosystems Resource Integration Center, PATRIC, is the legacy Bacterial Bioinformatics Resource Center (BRC), representing 15 years of progressive development and service to bacterial researchers. PATRIC contains hundreds of thousands of consistently annotated genomes and freely available tools for genome assembly, annotation, and comparative analysis; phylogenetics; transcriptomics; metagenomics; and others. PATRIC also provides a private workspace into which users can upload and analyze their own data and a command line interface for programmatic access to tools and data.</p>
